          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-mackay" title="Mr James Mackay">The Lord Chancellor</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I beg to move Amendments No. 3, 4 and 5:
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03330'>
