        <q>("(2) A person falls within this subsection in relation to a child if
        <ol>
        <li>(a) he is a parent of the child, or</li>
        <li>(b) he has or has had parental responsibility for the child.").</li>
        </ol></q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03331'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0563P0_19950424_GCR_42' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 2, line 6, at end insert&#x2014;
        <q>("() In a case where a child has been adopted or has been freed for adoption by virtue of any of the enactments mentioned in section 16(1) of the <a href="/acts/adoption-act-1976">Adoption Act 1976</a>, two persons are also associated with each other for the purposes of this Act if&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) one is a natural parent of the child or a parent of such a natural parent, and</li>
