      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_9gc' title='Col. 9GC &mdash; HL Deb 24 April 1995 vol 563 c9GC' name='column_9gc' href='#column_9gc' rel='bookmark'>9GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03334'>
