      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03336'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0563P0_19950424_GCR_47' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 7 [<span class="italic">Occupation orders where applicant has estate or interest etc, or has matrimonial home rights</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03337'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0563P0_19950424_GCR_48' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">The Lord Chancellor</span> moved Amendments No. 6:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03338'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0563P0_19950424_GCR_49' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
