        Schedule 4 [<span class="italic">Transfer of certain tenancies on divorce etc. or on separation of cohabitants</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0563P0-03549'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0563P0_19950424_GCR_260' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
